                            <comment id="13092075" author="stack" created="Fri, 26 Aug 2011 21:40:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also think that our roll on 1 hour is too long.. we should roll more frequently, or else, undo the check for removal of old logs such that it can run independent of whether a roll or not.  Thats another issue though.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
